{"tid":2266464,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[尋人jj] 我朋友想搵返琴晚3am係旺角搭小巴返大埔既你","createTime":"2020-11-01T10:33:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-01T10:54:40.000Z","uid":3954,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"853402727af21bf19733ecb2fd6a68811502e9d3","tid":2266464,"uid":3954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T10:33:43.000Z","msg":"是咁的...<br />\n<br />\n琴晚3am左右係旺角搭小巴番大埔 坐隔離個男仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n男仔：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我朋友：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我朋友玩得太攰係小巴到不停釣魚...<br />\n<br />\n男仔：洗唔洗借個膊頭俾你挨下 見你好似好攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n由於我朋友太攰 好順口咁講左句：唔洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後我朋友醒返 諗緊點算好 洗唔洗同佢講返野之際 個男仔就落左車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家我好後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw多謝你借個膊頭俾我挨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然我無挨到 希望搵得番你 想多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f02612a18e6c55cf0684c54dd7ca2393c4985d17","tid":2266464,"uid":21483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T10:34:46.000Z","msg":"Gay<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"392d2583a1e398c1146846f245dd9aaa60defb78","tid":2266464,"uid":283984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T10:35:20.000Z","msg":"player識唔到就next啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要回頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfba555949f2342116cb9ab7bc8e9cd648b4bc91","tid":2266464,"uid":3954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f02612a18e6c5